Package: elementary-default-settings
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, elementary-icon-theme
Recommends: pantheon-terminal, noise
Replaces: midori, midori-gtk3, midori-granite, libgtk-3-0
Enhances: midori, midori-gtk3, midori-granite, plank
Description: elementary default settings
 This package contains various system defaults for elementary OS.
 Installing this package won't affect existing users on your system.

Package: elementary-dpms-helper
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, x11-xserver-utils
Description: script and settings for X DPMS
 Basic script and GSettings for managing
 X Display Power Management Signaling when
 GNOME Settings Daemon's Power plugin should not.

Package: elementary-live-settings
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, elementary-default-settings
Description: configuration for the elementary OS live cd
 This package contains live cd customizations used by elementary OS.

